   The user is running the Ralph autonomous loop (`scripts/ralph/CLAUDE.md`) on the Marketify project (mobile marketplace MVP: Expo + React Native + Supabase). The explicit task: pick the lowest-priority `passes: false` story and implement it end-to-end following the Ralph protocol (orient → implement → quality gates → code review → mobile verification → commit → mark passes:true → update progress.txt). Target story is **US-046 — Submission composer screen**. Acceptance criteria: (1) `app/(creator)/submit/[applicationId].tsx` with URL input in mono font, live oEmbed preview (thumbnail + caption), checklist for post-conditions; (2) Submit button disabled until URL valid + all conditions checked; (3) On success: toast + route to Submitted tab; (4) Mobile-mcp verification pasting a real TikTok URL with screenshots; (5) Commit.

